No. D-2492. In the Matter of Discipline of Patrick D. McNeal. 561 U.S. 1045, 131 S. Ct. 43,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1133,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5554. July 26, 2010.

Patrick D. McNeal, of Santa Ana, California, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
